<item>
            <title>[LU-19768] add jobstats, brw_stats, others to netlink/YAML output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19768</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Lustre stats collection via Netlink/YAML is incomplete.  It is not currently possible to access statistics from non-&quot;stat&quot; files, such as &lt;tt&gt;md_stats&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;jobstats&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;brw_stats&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;These (and other) statistics need to be accessible via Netlink in order to provide a comprehensive monitoring interface for Lustre without having to scrape and parse text output via &lt;tt&gt;lctl&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="94731">LU-19768</key>
            <summary>add jobstats, brw_stats, others to netlink/YAML output</summary>
                <type id="4" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11310&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Improvement</type>
